task.summary: Default task
added git ignore, and deleted cmake-build-debug
Finished the basic model class, and set the program so it render's cubes
I refactored the Model class, into the ModelMesh class. Soon I will write a new Model class, but it will be made up of multiple ModelMeshes.
Made a small change, so the system now supports loading .dae files.
Deleted some extra unused stuff from the main, and add two object files
Added a Transformation class, and changed the model, and modelmesh classes to use it.
I have animations working, but they have a distortion when moving in some directions
I fixed the bug in the animation system
I made the project compile with wall werror wextra, I need to set cmake up so that it downloads dependencies when it builds the makefiles
I fixed a strange afterimage glitch in with the animation, and added rotation animation.
Added an assert to the add keyframe function in the animation class.
I fixed something that cased a crash on windows, and programed a cool animation

Changed the main so that it tries to display multiple models based on the same meshes on the screen at once. I realized that the models cannot delete the meshes in the destructors because the meshes might be used by other models.
The shader class now triggers an assert when it calls it's destructor, I'm not sure why.
I fixed the assignment operator, and copy constructor in all the classes coping is now only allowed for certain classes. I also added one line in the main to help with gui support
Fixed the bug in the shader class
I accidentally reverted this branch back to a previous verion, and I had to fix the main
I fixed the bug in the shader class.
I made progress with the window manager, and the renderer.
I have resolution scaling working. It just break's in full screen mode some times.
Added a model dispenser class that does the job of managing model mesh's and placed the shader inside the renderer class.
Switched the library so that it builds a library file, instead of an exe
fixed a bug in the model's copy constructer, and fixed an uninitialized variable error, and fixed an error with the asserts in the window class.
Fixed the model positions
Fixed a bug in the animation class
Added extra error sensitivity to cmake
added climits to the file
Fixed another two platform specific bugs
Added AA and anisotropic filtering
Fixed a bug where valid resolutions were duplicated.
